<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/seo-head', { seo }) %>
<% if (false) { %>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Taxi from Jaipur | Outstation Cab & Car Rental | Rajasthali Tours</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Book taxi from Jaipur to any destination across India. Outstation cab, car rental, and tour packages. 500+ luxury vehicles. Govt-approved, IATA-certified. ₹1,600 onwards. Call +91 97853 07799.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="taxi from Jaipur, outstation cab Jaipur, car rental Jaipur, Jaipur taxi service, cab from Jaipur, Jaipur to all cities taxi, outstation taxi Jaipur, Jaipur cabs, Rajasthali Tours">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://rajasthalitours.com/taxi-from-jaipur">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Taxi from Jaipur — Outstation Cab & Car Rental | Rajasthali Tours">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Book taxi from Jaipur to 30+ destinations across India. Luxury cars, SUVs, coaches. Govt-approved. ₹1,600 onwards.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://rajasthalitours.com/taxi-from-jaipur">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://rajasthalitours.com/rajasthalitours_images/hero_rajasthan.png">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/rajasthalitours_images/logo.png">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/seo-pages.css">

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://rajasthalitours.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Taxi from Jaipur", "item": "https://rajasthalitours.com/taxi-from-jaipur" }
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "name": "Rajasthali Tours & Travels Pvt. Ltd.",
    "url": "https://rajasthalitours.com",
    "telephone": "+919785307799",
    "email": "reservation@rajasthalitours.com",
    "description": "Rajasthali Tours is Jaipur's leading outstation taxi and cab service. 500+ luxury vehicles, govt-approved, IATA-certified. Serving 30+ destinations across India.",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "43, Shopping Complex, Ambabari",
      "addressLocality": "Jaipur",
      "addressRegion": "Rajasthan",
      "postalCode": "302039",
      "addressCountry": "IN"
    },
    "geo": { "@type": "GeoCoordinates", "latitude": 26.9124, "longitude": 75.7873 },
    "openingHours": "Mo-Su 00:00-23:59",
    "priceRange": "₹₹",
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.8",
      "reviewCount": "3200",
      "bestRating": "5"
    }
  }
  </script>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do I book a taxi from Jaipur?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Call +91 97853 07799 or WhatsApp us with your destination, date, number of passengers, and preferred vehicle. We confirm within 30 minutes with a fixed price quote." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the cheapest taxi from Jaipur?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Our most economical option is the Swift Dzire sedan starting from ₹1,600 for Ajmer (135 km). All fares include toll, fuel, and driver — no hidden charges." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you offer round-trip taxis from Jaipur?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We offer one-way, round-trip with waiting, and outstation packages (cab with driver waiting for 2–5 days) for any destination from Jaipur." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which is the best taxi company in Jaipur?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Rajasthali Tours & Travels is Jaipur's most trusted taxi and tour operator — govt-approved, IATA-certified, with 500+ vehicles and 15+ years of experience serving 10,000+ happy customers." }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
</head>
<% } %>
<body class="seo-body">

  <%- include('partials/seo-header') %>

  <section class="seo-hero">
    <div class="seo-hero-inner">
      <nav class="seo-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span>›</span>
        <span>Taxi from Jaipur</span>
      </nav>

      <div class="seo-badge">GOVERNMENT APPROVED · IATA CERTIFIED · SINCE 2010</div>
      <h1 class="seo-hero-title">
        Taxi from <span class="seo-highlight">Jaipur</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="seo-hero-sub">
        Book outstation cab, car rental, or tour packages from Jaipur to <strong>30+ destinations</strong> across Rajasthan, Delhi, Agra, Haridwar, Shimla, Varanasi, and all of India. Professional chauffeurs, luxury vehicles, transparent pricing.
      </p>

      <div class="seo-hero-stats">
        <div class="seo-stat"><span class="seo-stat-num">30+</span><span class="seo-stat-label">Destinations</span></div>
        <div class="seo-stat"><span class="seo-stat-num">500+</span><span class="seo-stat-label">Vehicles</span></div>
        <div class="seo-stat"><span class="seo-stat-num">₹1,600</span><span class="seo-stat-label">Starting Fare</span></div>
        <div class="seo-stat"><span class="seo-stat-num">24/7</span><span class="seo-stat-label">Available</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+919785307799" class="seo-cta-primary">📞 Book Taxi Now</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919785307799?text=Hi%2C%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%20taxi%20from%20Jaipur." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="seo-cta-secondary">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-section" style="background: #0f0f1a;">
    <div class="seo-container">
      <h2 class="seo-section-title">Fleet Options & Rates</h2>
      <p class="seo-section-sub">All fares include: driver, fuel, tolls, parking, and state permits. No hidden charges.</p>

      <div class="vehicle-grid">
        <div class="vehicle-card">
          <div class="vehicle-icon">🚗</div>
          <h3>Economy Sedan</h3>
          <p class="vehicle-name">Swift Dzire / Toyota Etios</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Up to 4 passengers</li>
            <li>Air conditioned</li>
            <li>25 kg luggage</li>
            <li>₹10–12/km for outstation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="vehicle-rate">From ₹1,600</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vehicle-card">
          <div class="vehicle-icon">🚙</div>
          <h3>Premium MUV</h3>
          <p class="vehicle-name">Toyota Innova Crysta</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Up to 6 passengers</li>
            <li>Captain seat comfort</li>
            <li>40 kg luggage</li>
            <li>₹15–18/km for outstation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="vehicle-rate">From ₹2,800</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vehicle-card">
          <div class="vehicle-icon">🛻</div>
          <h3>Luxury SUV</h3>
          <p class="vehicle-name">Toyota Fortuner</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Up to 7 passengers</li>
            <li>4WD for hill stations</li>
            <li>50 kg luggage</li>
            <li>₹20–24/km for outstation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="vehicle-rate">From ₹4,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vehicle-card">
          <div class="vehicle-icon">🚌</div>
          <h3>Tempo Traveller</h3>
          <p class="vehicle-name">12 to 17 Seater</p>
          <ul>
            <li>10–17 passengers</li>
            <li>Reclining push-back seats</li>
            <li>Group & family tours</li>
            <li>₹18–22/km for outstation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="vehicle-rate">From ₹6,000</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-section" style="background: #080810;">
    <div class="seo-container">
      <h2 class="seo-section-title">Popular Taxi Routes from Jaipur</h2>
      <p class="seo-section-sub">Click any destination to view full route details, attractions, and pricing.</p>

      <div class="route-grid">
        <% const rajasthan = destinations.filter(d => d.region === 'Rajasthan'); %>
        <% const panIndia = destinations.filter(d => d.region !== 'Rajasthan'); %>

        <div class="route-group">
          <h3 class="route-group-title">🏜️ Rajasthan</h3>
          <% rajasthan.forEach(function(d) { %>
          <a href="/tours/<%= d.slug %>" class="route-row">
            <div class="route-info">
              <span class="route-name">Jaipur → <%= d.name %></span>
              <span class="route-detail"><%= d.distance %> km · <%= d.driveTime %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="route-fare">From ₹<%= (Math.round(d.distance * 11 / 100) * 100) %></div>
          </a>
          <% }); %>
        </div>

        <div class="route-group">
          <h3 class="route-group-title">🇮🇳 Pan-India</h3>
          <% panIndia.forEach(function(d) { %>
          <a href="/tours/<%= d.slug %>" class="route-row">
            <div class="route-info">
              <span class="route-name">Jaipur → <%= d.name %></span>
              <span class="route-detail"><%= d.distance %> km · <%= d.driveTime %> · <%= d.region %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="route-fare">From ₹<%= (Math.round(d.distance * 12 / 100) * 100) %></div>
          </a>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-section" style="background: #0f0f1a;">
    <div class="seo-container">
      <h2 class="seo-section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="seo-faqs">
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>How do I book a taxi from Jaipur?</h3>
          <p>Call <a href="tel:+919785307799">+91 97853 07799</a> or WhatsApp us with your destination, travel date, number of passengers, and preferred vehicle. We confirm with a fixed price quote within 30 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>What is the starting taxi fare from Jaipur?</h3>
          <p>The lowest fare is ₹1,600 for short routes like Jaipur to Ajmer (135 km) in a sedan. All fares include driver, fuel, tolls, and parking — no hidden charges. Call for exact quotes on any route.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>Do you offer one-way and round-trip taxis?</h3>
          <p>Yes. We offer one-way, round-trip (driver waits and returns), and multi-day outstation packages. For tours of 2–7 days, our driver stays with you throughout at no extra charge (driver allowance included).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>Do you pick up from Jaipur airport and railway station?</h3>
          <p>Yes. We provide 24/7 pickup from Jaipur International Airport (JAI), Jaipur Railway Station, and all major hotels. Our drivers track flight arrivals and adjust for delays automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>Which vehicle is best for a family road trip from Jaipur?</h3>
          <p>For families of 4–5, the Toyota Innova Crysta is our most popular choice — spacious, comfortable, and equipped with AC. For 6–7 pax or a hill station trip, the Toyota Fortuner is recommended.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-faq">
          <h3>Do you offer outstation cab for 7 days or more?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Our Rajasthan circuits (7–14 days) and pan-India tour packages include the vehicle for the full duration. Our longest running package is the 14-day Char Dham Yatra from Jaipur.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-cta-section">
    <div class="seo-container">
      <h2>Book Your Jaipur Taxi in Under 2 Minutes</h2>
      <p>Call us with your requirements — we'll quote a fixed price and confirm your cab instantly.</p>
      <div class="seo-hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+919785307799" class="seo-cta-primary">📞 +91 97853 07799</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919785307799?text=Hi%2C%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%20taxi%20from%20Jaipur." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="seo-cta-secondary">💬 WhatsApp Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/seo-footer') %>
</body>
</html>
